version_description: This alternative version for novice players that allows for a key change without the more difficult barre chords.

There's no tabs of duet Dolly / Kenny on UG, so I just compiled existing versions and add modulation in G after 1st refrain plus I changed few details. In their live version, key is B. I hope that it'll be useful.
